    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for anyone needing a dependable daily driver. While the engine and transmission are solid and have been regularly serviced, the exterior shows some signs of its age, including minor dents and clear coat fading on the hood. The interior is clean but shows typical wear on the driver's seat and carpet. It\u2019s a great, honest car for someone who prioritizes mechanical function over aesthetic perfection.",
