      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. This example boasts addressed preventative maintenance, including the essential rear subframe reinforcement and VANOS system overhaul. The individual throttle bodies provide immediate induction response, while the factory limited-slip differential ensures optimal power delivery. The chassis remains rigid and communicative, with refreshed suspension bushings ensuring precise turn-in. A well-sorted driver\u2019s car for the purist who values mechanical integrity and linear power delivery.",
